<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, June 5 (Xinhua) -- The British Foreign Office announced
here Friday afternoon that it was planning an airlift to evacuate
its citizens from Eritrea while the border clashes between Eritrea
and Ethiopia continued worsening.
</P>
