<HEADLINE> Annan Calls for Negotiated Solution to Kosovo Question </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, June 5 (Xinhua) -- U.N. Secretary-General Kofi
Annan reiterates his call for a negotiated settlement to the
dispute over Kosovo, his spokesman told reporters here Friday.
</P>
<P>
