<HEADLINE> Greece Completes Report on Cause of Plane Crash </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, June 5 (Xinhua) -- Greece has completed a report on the
cause of a Ukrainian passenger plane which crashed in northern
Greece in December last year.
</P>
<P>
Greek Transport and Communications Minister Tassos Mandelis
said Friday that the report, which will also be handed to the
Ukrainian and Russian governments for comments, would be submitted
to the Greek supreme investigative council for air accidents, but
he did not reveal the findings of the report, the semi-official
Athens News Agency (ANA) reported.
</P>
