crashed into the mountains near Thessaloniki, northern Greece,
killing all 72 people on board.
</P>
<P>
To force Ukrainian Airline to pay relatives of a victim killed
in the incident, Greece has since earlier this year confiscated a
Ukrainian Airlines passenger plane. 
