Pakistan and India) is held it is practically reduced to the
dialogue of the death," he noted.
</P>
<P>
"The situation has been exacerbated as a result of a
nuclearized South Asia, so the need is felt ever more for the
dialogue which takes us somewhere which brings us the solution of
the root-cause -- the Kashmir issue," he said. 
