<HEADLINE> Philippines to Host World Expo 2002 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, June 6 (Xinhua) -- President Fidel Ramos said here
Saturday that the Philippines has won its bid to host the
prestigious World Expo 2002.
</P>
<P>
The victory of the Philippines over Australia marked the first
time that a developing country was chosen by the 84-member
countries of the Bureau of International Expositions (BIE) as the
site of the trade exposition, the Philippine News Agency said.
</P>
<P>
