<HEADLINE> World Bank Supports Zimbabwe's National Parks </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, June 6 (Xinhua) -- Zimbabwe's Department of National
Parks and Wild Life Management will get 70 million U.S.Dollars
from the World Bank to promote its rehabilitation and
conservation project for national parks, the Herald reported
Saturday.
</P>
