the people of the region. India should now forget for ever the
idea to subjugate Kashmiris and continue its occupation of
Kashmir," he said.
</P>
<P>
"A new world is emerging after nuclear tests and now the
international community is realizing the threats to the peace of
South Asia," he said.
</P>
<P>
The world, he said, is now paying attention to the Kashmir
dispute and they are feeling that South Asia could not see peace
until the Kashmir dispute is settled.
</P>
<P>
"We have been conveying this message to the world for 50 years
and this was the message of our nuclear explosions," he said.
