dollars, a 9.9 percent increase over the previous year, it said.
</P>
<P>
The Brazilian trade deficit was 6.3 billion dollars in 1997.
</P>
<P>
Brazil-U.S. trade exchange rose rapidly in the last four years.
</P>
<P>
