"Xinhua Daily Telegraph"
</P>
<P>
-- Vice-Premier Li Lanqing urged the whole nation to give more
importance to the strategy of revitalizing China through science
and education. Li made the remark at the closing ceremony of a
high-profile conference attended by members of the Chinese Academy
of Sciences (CAS) and the Chinese Academy of Engineering (CAE).
</P>
<P>
